            "For biomes, link climate (rainfall, temperature) to vegetation and adaptations (e.g. savanna: seasonal rain → grasses + fire-resistant trees).",
            "Use Zimbabwe/southern Africa examples: savanna biome, Hwange, CAMPFIRE, deforestation, soil types.",
